─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Foundational research
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

PriorStudio implements the Prior-Data Fitted Networks paradigm
introduced in:

  Müller, Hollmann, Pineda, Hutter — "Transformers Can Do Bayesian
  Inference". ICLR 2022. https://arxiv.org/abs/2112.10510

The prior interface, training loop, and reference implementations are
faithful ports of patterns established in the AutoML group's PFNs
library (https://github.com/automl/PFNs, Apache-2.0). We are grateful
to the authors for publishing their work openly.


