Several project templates in `priors/` and packaged in the studio
marketplace are derived from publicly licensed research code. Each
template's README lists its upstream source and license. None of
PriorStudio's code is a binary fork; every template is a fresh
implementation that follows the upstream's published prior spec and
attribution requirements.

