                        Hoo, Müller, Hollmann et al. (arXiv 2501.02945)

  MotherNet             Apache-2.0    microsoft/mothernet
                        Müller, Curino, Ramakrishnan (arXiv 2312.08598)

  PFNs4BO               Apache-2.0    automl/PFNs4BO
