─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Third-party Python dependencies
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Dependencies are listed in each package's pyproject.toml under
[project.dependencies] and [project.optional-dependencies]. Notable
runtime dependencies include numpy (BSD-3-Clause), pydantic
(MIT), pyyaml (MIT), and torch (BSD-3-Clause, optional). The complete
license list and version constraints are reproduced in the lockfile
when the package is installed.
